307 Mission Ln is listed for rent at $ 2,000. The Rental - Townhouse Condominium property has 3 bedrooms, 3 Full Bathrooms, 1530 square feet and was built in 2014. The lot size is 1450 Square feet. ##BR##You will not want to miss this stunning three bedroom townhome located in the heart of East End! Located in a small, gated, charming community, this property features everything you will need for convenient living, including recent fresh paint, fridge, washer and dryer included and a two car garage! The kitchen features beautiful granite countertops with stainless appliances, kitchen island with bar seating and loads of cabinet and counter space. About this property

You will not want to miss this stunning three bedroom townhome located in the heart of East End! Located in a small, gated, charming community, this property features everything you will need for convenient living, including recent fresh paint, fridge, washer and dryer included and a two car garage! The kitchen features beautiful granite countertops with stainless appliances, kitchen island with bar seating and loads of cabinet and counter space. You will have plenty of privacy with a spacious bedroom and full bath on the first floor. Second floor features second bedroom, with a full bath alongside the stunning primary suite. Master is complete with a luxurious en-suite bathroom and an oversized walk in closet! Just minutes away is downtown, shopping, coffee shops and a vibrant nightlife, putting you in the center of it all! Dont wait, schedule your showing today!

Listen to the Audio Tour

307 Mission Ln is listed for rent at $ 2,000. The Rental - Townhouse Condominium property has 3 bedrooms, 3 Full Bathrooms, 1530 square feet and was built in 2014. The lot size is 1450 Square feet. ##BR##You will not want to miss this stunning three bedroom townhome located in the heart of East End! Located in a small, gated, charming community, this property features everything you will need for convenient living, including recent fresh paint, fridge, washer and dryer included and a two car garage! The kitchen features beautiful granite countertops with stainless appliances, kitchen island with bar seating and loads of cabinet and counter space. You will have plenty of privacy with a spacious bedroom and full bath on the first floor. Second floor features second bedroom, with a full bath alongside the stunning primary suite. Master is complete with a luxurious en-suite bathroom and an oversized walk in closet! Just minutes away is downtown, shopping, coffee shops and a vibrant nightlife, putting you in the center of it all! Dont wait, schedule your showing today!

The percentage (often as high as 1% of the loan amount) that a lending institution charges for processing and originating a loan.

PMI %

						

						
					

					
If your downpayment is less than 20% of the value of the home you are buying, you may be required to pay mortgage insurance of somewhere between 0.2% and 0.5% of your principal balance each month. Enter .04% simply as .4 (do not include percent sign).
